                <note type="abstract">In his appendices the author includes edited excerpts from al-Qirqisānī’s Judaeo-Arabic commentary (which includes sporadic glosses of the biblical text) on Gen 1:1–3, 11, 17–18, 20–21, 26, 28, 30; 2:2, 7, 16, 21; 3:1; 4:7; 6:2, 13, 16; and from Yefet’s Judaeo-Arabic translation (the separate Judaeo-Arabic translation of which is not always included, though snippets and glosses are usually still found in the commentary) and commentary on Gen 1:1–7, 20, 25–27, 30; 2:1–3, 7, 9, 16–17, 21; 3:1, 8, 15, 17, 22–24; 4:6–7; 6:5; 8:21; 12:2; 15:1, 5; 19:11; 22:1, 12; 27:19; 30:38; 41:7; Exod 3:15; 4:1, 3–4, 8–9, 14; 11:4; 12:13; 15:25–26; 19:3, 20; 20:1–3, 5–6, 9; 21:34; 24:10–11; 34:18–20; 35:3; Num 12:6–8; 14:18; 20:12–13; 22:6, 12, 28–30; 23:5; Deut 3:26; 4:6, 39; 5:21–23; 6:4; 11:26–29; 21:3; 30:6, 19; 32:7, 39, 50; 34:9; 1 Sam 28:8–25; Isa 40:22; 41:1; 43:10; 45:7; 46:8–10; 47:9–10; 51:6; 55:1–2; 59:13; 63:17; 64:3; 66:1–2; Jer 8:7; 32:19; 44:25; Ezek 3:6, 19–21; 14:5; 18:32; 37:9, 13–14; Obad 1:3; Jonah 4:10–11; Hab 2:18; Zech 1:8; Pss 8:3, 6; 9:18; 14:2–3; 19:10; 26:2; 28:5; 32:1–2; 49:11; 50:1; 59:6; 68:5; 89:7; 94:8–9; 103:20–22; 104:2, 4–5, 31–32; 11:10; 119:18, 89–91; 135:6; 139:1–5, 14, 19–22; 145:15, 17; Prov 3:12; 8:4–9, 22–23, 30–32; 10:8–9; 16:4–5, 25; 17:3, 5; 18:14; 22:4; 24:16–18; 30:1–6; Job 1:13–19; 2:10; 5:7; 9:3–4; 11:7; 12:7–8; 15:15–16; 23:8–9; 28:12–13, 27–28; 37:23.</note>
